CTetris:

    "CTetris" stands for C of Teteris

Naming Convention:
    Lowercase   Capitalization  Uppercase
    ctetris     CTetris         CTETRIS 

Docs:
    * http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/tetris

Language:
    * c

Library/API:
    * ISO C99
    * GNU C Library
    * ncurses

Build System:
    * GNU Make
